These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-7-1::.
7 different games are played: canasta, billiard, scrabble, snooker, whist, poker, monopoly
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, marigold, sunflower, balloon-flower, zinnia, bellflower
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, disco, folk, metal, pop, reggae
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, pink, aquamarine, yellow, light-blue, fuchsia, azure
 1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
 3. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is the fan of folk##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing billiard is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
