11. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
12. the person playing billiard is the fan of blues##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere between the person who growsazalea and the person who growspoppy##7
14. the person who likes blood-red is in the middle##1
15. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
16. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
17. the person who likes blood-red is the person who growssunflower##1
18. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of pop##1
19. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5
20. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
21. the person who likes yellow is the fan of metal##1
